Enkai o ltung'ana lenyena


1  Isipat ajoito tiatua Kristo, malejisho nanu; naaishakenoki nanu oltau lai te Nkiyang'et Sinyati, 
2  nchere kaara sapuk oleng osina o emion ti atua oltau lai. 
3  Amu ketaa kayieu napaji naa nanu makewan edeki naadung'ori aarishie Kristo te nkaraki lalashera, laainei entalipa o lorere lai. 
4   Isiraeli ninche, naa ninche eitaa nkera enyena, neisho enkitoo, ilkulenye isotuaitin, ninche eishooki Nkitanapat, o esayiata e Nkai o nkisiligat enyena; 
5  ilkulenye iloo Akuiyiaa, naa ole ilo orere Kristo. Metamayiani Enkai natii shumata pooki ntarasi. Esai.


6  Kake mme taa doi keetae enaturua ororei le Nkai. Amu mme Siraeli ate lelo pooki le ishoi e Siraeli, 
7   neme nkera e Abraham lelo pooki le ishoi enye; kake, “Nkera e Isaak eji nkera inono.” 
8  Nejo ina nchere mme nena kera o sesen naara nne Nkai, kake nkera e nkisiligata enye eikenakini aajo eishoi enye. 
9   Amu inji etejo enkisiligata enye, “Kalotu kenya tena rishata netum Sara enkayioni.” 
10  Neme neijia ake, kake inoolpayian obo papa lang Isaak nkera e Rebeka. 
11  Kake, ore meino eton eitu eas ninche ae supat aashu entorrono, ore eji peyie eitobirari eyieunoto e Nkai o engelunoto enye, neme te nkaraki isiaaitin kake te nkaraki e nkipototo enye, 
12   nejokini Rebeka, “Keaku olbotor oisiaai oloti.” 
13   Anaa enatisiraki aajo, “Yakobo atonyorra kake aibayie Esau.”


14  Aikijo aa iyiook? Aikijo mme asipani Enkai te nkiguana enye? Mme neijia pae! 
15   Amu etiaaka ninye Musa, “Nanu oing'urrie olayieu naing'urrie, naitanana oshoke to layieu naduaya.” 
16  Ore pooki nemeigarakino enayieu oltung'ani, kake eigarakino olng'ur le Nkai. 
17   Amu etiaakita Ilkigerot Farao, “Nanu laailepie naa kajo paa te iyie aitoduaaya engolon ai, nelikiori enkarna ai tiatua enkop pooki.” 
18  Neaku ninye oing'urrie oloyieu neing'urrie, neitagol oltau lo loyieu neitagol.

Engoro e Nkai o lng'ur lenye


19  Naa ore taata nikijoki, “Oo naa pee eitokini ake aajo eitarruoitie ltung'ana?” Ae ng'ae oidim aibooi eyieunoto enye? 
20   Kake aira ng'ae lo tung'ani owaliki Enkai? Kejoki entoki naitobiruni ilo oitobirita, “Oo pee kintayio aikunu inji? 
21  Eimeitore esarng'ab oloitobiru motioo e sarng'ab, neitainyie ae entoki sidai nashili, neitobirie ae entoki ake naasishoreki? 
22  Oo te naa Enkai nayieu, ejo pee etumoki aitoduaai engoro enye neyiolouni sii engolon enye, netang'asa ang'iriaki oleng lelo oora ile ngoro laa enkitarruorroto ake eitobirakaki, 
23  naa ore pee eyiolouni eneba enkarsisisho e nkitoo enye te lelo laa olng'ur eitobirakaki, naa ninye sii oitera aitobiraki ninche te dukuya te nkitoo enye, 
24  iyiook taa lelo laa ninye oitopiwuo, neme too Lyahudi ake kake too Loreren sii?” 
25   Nesipa etejo ninye te Hosea,

“Iltung'ana apa leme laainei ayooki nanu aipot ajo,

‘ltung'ana laainei’, ore apa ina tinki

nayooki nanu ajo, ‘Enkirotet ai.’ ”


26   “Ore te napa ake wueji netiaakinyeki

ninche, ‘Mirara ltung'ana laainei’ te ina

eyookini aajo ninche ‘Nkera e Nkai naishu.’ ”


27   Netabuaa Isaya ajo ti alo Siraeli: “Ore hoo neba nkera e Siraeli anaa osinyai le naiposha, oloti pisiai ake eitajeuni ti atua ninche; 
28  amu keitabaiki Enkai enkop enkiguana natudung'oko asioki o te ngolon.” 
29   Naa ore anaa enatoduaa Isaya, “Te neme Olaitoriani loo lororani otelekaka iyiook nkera, anaata kitotiutuo anaa Sodom, neikoni iyiook anaa Gomora.”

Enkomono e Paulo te nkaraki Isiraeli


30  Aikijo aa naa iyiook? Iloreren leitu eing'oru ninche esupatisho ninche oonoto, naa to rrekie le nkirukoto; 
31  kake eji ore ninche Siraeli ooing'orutua esupatisho aa nekua kitanapat eitasheyie neitu eidim ninche aaitabai nena kitanapat. 
32  Aainyo? Enkaraki neitu eing'oru to rrekie le nkirukoto, kake etiu anaa too nkiaasin. Ketarrorrote te ilo soit orrorrisho, 
33   anaa enatisiraki, “Ng'ura, nanu oirragie te Sion osoit orror iltung'ana, osoit kitok obatat ninche, kake ore oloiruk ninye nemeitukurruni.”

